snippet.title: Persona 3 Reload - English Gameplay Reveal | Xbox Game Pass, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows PC
snippet.description:
We’ve been waiting for this - new Persona 3 Reload gameplay footage featuring the first look at our English VO cast has been shown at Anime Expo! 

Stay tuned for more Persona 3 Reload reveals during each month’s Full Moon! 🌕
